  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t如题，大家都知道，习畜现在做的一系列加速行为都是在拙劣地模仿它的野爹腊肉。然而现在习畜在形体，举止，眼神，行走动作上也已经高度看齐腊肉了。看看下面维基的照片，就连神态也是高度相似。<br/>\n<br/>\n正如金三胖对金大胖的形象模仿，可以起到信仰传承的作用。习畜做梦都想达成毛的那种一句空头支票就让几亿人为它疯狂的独裁程度，它会不会也梳一头它野爹那样的发型，然后配上它爹经常穿的衣服（在天安门上就穿了哈哈哈）<br/>\n参考图如下<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2MwZGRlYmYzMjU2N2M4YjgzNTk5LmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMzc2JmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc0ddebf32567c8b83599.jpg?width=2376&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc0ddebf32567c8b83599.jpg?width=2376&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc0ddebf32567c8b83599.jpg?width=2376&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDQxYjMyYzU3NDU3ODM4Y2QwNmRkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMzc2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/041b32c57457838cd06dd.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/041b32c57457838cd06dd.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/041b32c57457838cd06dd.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2U2ODFmZTE3ZTgxYWY0NGEwODlmLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMzc2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e681fe17e81af44a089f.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e681fe17e81af44a089f.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e681fe17e81af44a089f.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2376\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
